20shown%20at%20a%20tennis%20club%2C%20to%20Tyler%20the%20Creator's%20prep-adjacent%20streetwear%20line%20Golf.%20Adidas%2C%20Lululemon%2C%20and%20Sun%20Day%20Red%20%E2%80%94%20the%20clothing%20line%20started%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiger-woods-wife-net-worth-majors-golf-pga%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETiger%20Woods%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20singlehandedly%20sparked%20a%20golf%20boom%20decades%20ago%20%E2%80%94%20all%20recently%20launched%20their%20own%20golf%20collections%20for%20women.%20And%20countless%20boutique%20designers%20have%20taken%20a%20new%20interest%20in%20elevating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-expensive-tennis-outfits-watches-photos-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etennis%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20golf%2C%20and%20ski%20wear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20these%20sports%20have%20moved%20away%20from%20solely%20being%20played%20in%20country%20clubs%20and%20elite%20backyards.%20Three-quarters%20of%20all%20golf%20courses%20are%20open%20to%20the%20public%20and%20off-course%20venues%20are%20booming.%20Golf%20simulators%20have%20surged%2073%25%20since%202019%2C%20and%20the%20entertainment%20driving%20range%2C%20Topgolf%2C%20doubled%20its%20revenue%20in%202021%20with%20additional%20increases%20in%20subsequent%20years.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftennis-usta-stop-pickleball-red-tennis-ball-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnited%20States%20Tennis%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E's%20Tennis%20Venue%20Services%20awarded%20%2410%20million%20in%20grants%20to%20repair%20public%20tennis%20courts%20and%20build%20new%20ones.%20%26quot%3BGen%20Z%20seems%20to%20be%20challenging%20time-honored%20exclusivity%20by%20engaging%20with%20these%20sports%20in%20public%20spaces%2C%20community-based%20clubs%2C%20and%20tech-driven%20alternatives%20like%20golf%20simulators%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Lewis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECaitlin%20Thompson%2C%20who%20founded%20the%20quarterly%20tennis%20magazine%20Racquet%20in%202016%2C%20has%20noticed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-open-popular-as-tennis-interest-surges-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboom%20in%20tennis%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20sport%20reached%20its%20highest-ever%20number%20of%20players%20in%202024%2C%20with%20one%20in%20every%2012%20Americans%20participating.%20It's%20grown%20by%2045%25%20since%202019.%20%26quot%3BPre-pandemic%2C%20we%20felt%20more%20like%20we%20were%20talking%20to%20a%20smaller%20group%20of%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20Now%2C%20it's%20a%20lot%20of%20beginners.%20Racquet's%20events%20are%20regularly%20packed%20with%20celebrities%20and%20tennis%20stars%2C%20attracting%20lengthy%20waiting%20lists.%20Its%20limited-edition%20merchandise%20drops%20sell%20out%20almost%20instantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELee's%20Hot%20Girl%20Golf%20Club%20is%20also%20struggling%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20demand%20%E2%80%94%20it%20has%20over%201%2C000%20people%20in%20the%20dedicated%20group%20chat.%20%26quot%3BWe%20sell%20out%20all%20of%20our%20events%2C%20sometimes%20within%20an%20hour%20or%20two%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20Attendees%20are%20mainly%20in%20their%2020s%20and%2030s.%20A%20big%20reason%2C%20Lee%20has%20found%2C%20is%20that%20women%20want%20to%20improve%20their%20skills%20and%20feel%20%26quot%3Bable%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20business%20conversations%20%E2%80%94%20not%20feeling%20left%20out%20of%20those%20elite%20circles.%26quot%3B%20There%20are%20also%20those%20who%20simply%20enjoy%20the%20cute%20outfits.%20%26quot%3BThat%20preppy%20girl%2C%20old-money%20vibe%20is%20definitely%20a%20draw%20for%20some%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20the%20case%20for%20Casey%20Forand.%20After%20spending%20some%20time%20at%20a%20driving%20range%2C%20the%2026-year-old%20played%20her%20first%20round%20of%20golf%20while%20on%20vacation%20in%20Florida%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago.%20%26quot%3BMy%20impression%20of%20golf%20was%20that%20it%20was%20super%20hard%20and%20intimidating%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20But%20after%20hitting%20a%20few%20fairways%2C%20she%20was%20invested%20and%20signed%20up%20for%20a%20county%20golf%20membership%20near%20her%20home%20in%20New%20Jersey.%20%26quot%3BI%20also%20love%20the%20old-money%20aesthetic%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20golf%20and%20country%20club%20culture%20is%20a%20huge%20part%20of%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnline%2C%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsofia-richie-style-how-to-dress-old-money-trend-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egilded%20luxury%20vibe%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20taken%20over.%20On%20TikTok%20and%20Instagram%2C%20videos%20and%20photos%20depicting%20young%20people%20in%20polos%20and%20pearls%2C%20with%20sweaters%20casually%20slung%20over%20their%20shoulders%20rack%20up%20millions%20of%20views.%20Often%2C%20they're%20playing%20sports%20like%20polo%2C%20tennis%2C%20and%20golf.%20Forand%20says%20her%20Instagram%20is%20now%20filled%20with%20ads%20for%20women's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feastside-golf-apparel-breaking-barriers-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egolf%20fashion%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20they%20are%20just%20there%20for%20the%20looks%2C%20the%20surge%20of%20young%20people%20in%20the%20walled%20garden%20of%20the%20wealthy%20is%20having%20real%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20room%20for%20so%20many%20newcomers%2C%20the%20sports%20have%20had%20to%20evolve.%20Thompson%20says%20one%20of%20the%20coolest%20things%20about%20the%20tennis%20boom%20is%20seeing%20new%20fans%20create%20lasting%20change.%20%26quot%3BThe%20more%20that%20the%20younger%20fans%20and%20creators%20and%20journalists%20have%20pushed%2C%20the%20more%20the%20sport%20has%20to%20modernize%2C%20not%20only%20the%20way%20that%20it%20allows%20access%20but%20also%20the%20way%20it%20talks