Fore%20Play%26quot%3B%20podcast%2C%20which%20bills%20itself%20as%20%26quot%3Bby%20the%20common%20golfer%2C%20for%20the%20common%20golfer%2C%26quot%3B%20has%20also%20led%20to%20what%20some%20call%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fnyysinatra%2Fstatus%2F1902469184228933882%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBarstool-ification%3C%2Fa%3E%20effect%20where%20entertainment%20and%20%26quot%3Bbro%20culture%26quot%3B%20are%20taking%20over%20more%20traditional%20norms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20average%20age%20on%20the%20links%20decreases%2C%20hot%20topics%20in%20club%20boardrooms%20now%20include%20whether%20music%20should%20be%20allowed%20on%20the%20course%20and%20whether%20dress%20codes%20should%20enforce%20tucked-in%20shirt%20rules.%20%26quot%3BThe%20clubs%20are%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20a%20way%20to%20appease%20everyone%20without%20turning%20away%20a%20younger%20potential%20member%20who's%20going%20to%20be%20there%20and%20paying%20dues%20for%20many%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Becker.%20%26quot%3BAs%20the%20older%20guard%20resigns%20and%20starts%20to%20move%20on%20from%20their%20private%20club%2C%20things%20will%20start%20to%20stabilize.%20Right%20now%20it's%20a%20challenge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChris%20Jenkins%2C%2053%2C%20from%20Colorado%2C%20has%20been%20playing%20golf%20for%20over%2030%20years%20and%20longs%20for%20the%20days%20before%20it%20became%20oversaturated.%20%26quot%3BI%20admit%20it%2C%20I'm%20the%20proverbial%20'get%20off%20my%20lawn'%20kind%20of%20guy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20get%20tee%20times%20or%20rounds%20now%20take%205%20%C2%BD%20hours.%20We%20blame%20all%20of%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Jenkins%2C%20the%20frustration%20isn't%20necessarily%20with%20the%20younger%20generation.%20It's%20more%20the%20tension%20that%20exists%20when%20any%20sport%20starts%20to%20gain%20popularity.%20%26quot%3BSneakers%20on%20the%20course%2C%20music%20%E2%80%94%20I%20don't%20like%20that.%20There%20are%20people%20that%20would%20say%2C%20'Oh%2C%20you're%2C%20like%2C%20country%20club%20snob'%20and%2C%20quite%20frankly%2C%20yes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20avoid%20the%20chaos%2C%20some%20golfers%20like%20Jenkins%20have%20joined%20country%20clubs%20so%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20suffer%20through%20slow%20rounds%20with%20rowdy%20golfers.%20%26quot%3BI%20do%20think%20that%20there's%20a%20level%20of%20%E2%80%94%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20say%20exclusivity%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it's%20a%20gentleman%20sport%2C%26quot%3B%20Jenkins%20says.%20If%20it%20were%20up%20to%20him%2C%20it%20would%20stay%20that%20way.%20%26quot%3BI%20get%20it%2C%20my%20generation%20is%20on%20the%20way%20out.%20But%20it%20doesn't%20mean%20I%20have%20to%20like%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThompson%20thinks%20the%20newcomers%20to%20tennis%2C%20whether%20they're%20drawn%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdestanee-aiava-wears-vintage-outfits-at-the-2025-australian-open-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecute%20clothes%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20the%20luxury%20aesthetic%2C%20are%20a%20value%20add%20for%20the%20sport.%20%26quot%3BWe%20did%20a%20big%20push%20into%20Korea%20last%20year%2C%20partially%20because%20people%20wanted%20to%20cosplay%20tennis%2C%20but%20then%20they%20started%20playing%20it%20and%20realized%20it%20was%20a%20fun%2C%20social%20way%20to%20connect%20with%20other%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20really%20amazing%20recreational%20and%20community%20offering.%20You%20don't%20get%20that%20if%20you%20just%20buy%20the%20Chateau%20Marmont%20keychain.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThompson%20also%20sees%20the%20old-money%20vibe%20dying%20off%20as%20more%20people%20flood%20the%20space%3A%20%26quot%3BAfter%20a%20certain%20period%20of%20time%2C%20there's%20only%20so%20many%20Princess%20Diana%20mood%20boards%20you%20can%20look%20at.%26quot%3B%20But%20she%20hopes%20the%20newfound%20fans%20will%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTh