.%20At%20the%20entrance%2C%20a%20military%20checkpoint%2C%20armed%20guards%20scanned%20passports%20and%20inspected%20cars.%20Several%20miles%20down%20the%20road%2C%20soldiers%20reviewed%20documents%20that%20granted%20visitors%20entry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20earlier%2C%20it%20was%20a%20much%20different%20scene%20here.%20On%20February%2024%2C%202022%2C%20Russian%20forces%20poured%20over%20the%20Belarusian%20border%20into%20Ukraine%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-troops-attack-through-chernobyl-exclusion-zone-risks-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecaptured%20Chernobyl%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20exclusion%20zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKireev%20recalled%20the%20day%20it%20happened%20and%20how%20a%20normal%20workday%20descended%20into%20chaos.%20His%20staff%20was%20evacuated%20by%20car%20and%20bus%20at%20about%207%20a.m.%20Two%20hours%20later%2C%20he%20was%20the%20only%20one%20left%20at%20the%20facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inside%20the%20abandoned%20city%20of%20Pripyat.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f7cdd9a466d2b74ab2c8bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20now%20abandoned%20city%20of%20Pripyat%2C%20once%20home%20to%2050%2C000%20people%2C%20had%20an%20amusement%20park.%3Cp%3EJake%20Epstein%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDetails%20were%20scarce%20at%20the%20time.%20He%20was%20told%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethat%20a%20situation%20was%20unfolding%20and%20that%20after%20a%20week%2C%20everyone%20could%20return%20to%20work.%20He%20left%20the%20exclusion%20zone%20later%20in%20the%20day%2C%20around%20noon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20took%20what%20we%20could%20with%20us%2C%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20not%20all%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20had%20known%20what%20it%20was%2C%20we%20would%20certainly%20have%20acted%20differe