ns%20to%20be%20a%20calling%20card%20for%20the%20country's%20film%20and%20TV%20prowess.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMBC%20Group%20founded%20the%20studio%20in%202018%20and%20brought%20in%20a%20former%20NBCUniversal%20exec%20to%20run%20it.%20MBC%20Studios%20soon%20began%20to%20jump%20into%20projects%20at%20a%20dizzying%20pace.%20By%20the%20time%20of%20the%202022%20audit%2C%20it%20had%20over%20100%20projects%20in%20various%20stages%20of%20production.%20The%20audit%2C%20which%20ran%20over%2050%20pages%2C%20said%20that%20while%20the%20studio%20was%20growing%20fast%2C%20it%20was%20undermined%20by%20unclear%20strategy%2C%20disorganization%2C%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20internal%20controls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20audit%20identified%20a%20litany%20of%20issues%2C%20including%20consultants%20hired%20without%20oversight%2C%20conflicts%20of%20interest%2C%20a%20lack%20of%20market%20research%2C%20and%20companies%20chosen%20outside%20a%20competitive%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20recommended%20tightening%20production%20practices%20to%20avoid%20overspending%2C%20hiring%20competitively%2C%20and%20monitoring%20projects'%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20that%20time%2C%20MBC%20Studios%20has%20had%20some%20wins%2C%20particularly%20with%20local-language%20productions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20five%20people%20close%20to%20the%20company%20told%20BI%20it%20has%20scaled%20back%20some%20of%20its%20original%20production%20ambitions%2C%20however.%20They%20said%20it's%20also%20been%20plagued%20by%20leadership%20shake-ups%20and%20jettisoned%20a%20series%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-hurt-hollywood-hopes-for-tv-movie-recovery-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHollywood%3C%2Fa%3E%20experts%20brought%20on%20to%20take%20its%20operations%20to%20the%20next%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20other%20big%20entertainment%20bet%20besides%20MBC%20Studios%2C%20Neom%20Media%20%E2%80%94%20the%20filmmaking%20facility%20in%20its%20futuristic%