E%26quot%3BKandahar%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20action%20film%20the%20studio%20funded%20starring%20Gerard%20Butler%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20first%20US%20films%20to%20be%20shot%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20was%20released%20in%202023%20to%20tepid%20reviews%20and%20a%20lackluster%20box%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221584%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gerard%20Butler%20in%20%26quot%3BKandahar%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f939fcc6ad288d147ded52%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221188%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGerard%20Butler-starring%20%26quot%3BKandahar%26quot%3B%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20US%20movies%20filmed%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3Cp%3EOpen%20Road%20Films%2FYouTube%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%2C%20the%20unreleased%20%26quot%3BDesert%20Warrior%2C%26quot%3B%20has%20been%20stymied%20by%20rising%20costs%20and%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDirected%20by%20British%20filmmaker%20Rupert%20Wyatt%2C%20who%20also%20made%20%26quot%3BRise%20of%20the%20Planet%20of%20the%20Apes%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BDesert%20Warrior%26quot%3B%20was%20the%20first%20feature%20film%20shot%20at%20Neom%20Media.%20By%20the%20time%20of%20the%202022%20audit%2C%20the%20budget%20had%20reached%20%24140%20million.%20People%20familiar%20with%20the%20financing%20characterized%20that%20as%20double%20its%20original%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20added%20costs%2C%20such%20as%20COVID%20protocols%2C%20were%20due%20to%20timing.%20Others%20were%20self-imposed.%20Infrastructure%20had%20to%20be%20built%20in%20the%20desert%2C%20and%20crew%20had%20to%20be%20flown%20in%20from%20other%20countries.%20The%20film%20went%20big%20on%20talent%2C%20enlisting%20Anthony%20Mackie%20of%20Marvel%20movie%20fame%20and%20Oscar%20winner%20Ben%20Kingsley%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20local%20stars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsiders%20said%20fights%20over%20creative%20direction%20and%20the%20film's%20length%20also%20hung%20up%20production.%20Filming%20ended%20in%202022%2C%20but%20there's%20been%20no%20festival%20premiere%20%E2%80%94%20the%20film%20will%20miss%20out%20on%20another%20Cannes%20Film%20Festival%20premiere%20this%20year%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20movie%20has%20yet%20to%20get%20a%20release%20date.%20That%20type%20of%20delay%20would%20be%20virtually%20unheard%20of%20in%20Hollywood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Image%20from%20Neom%20film%20production%20brochure%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f93a25c6ad288d147ded64%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22690%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Neom%20brochure%20touts%20its%20film%20production%20facilities%20as%20world-class.%3Cp%3ENeom%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2285ba82c0-202f-4e4b-9041-2958800526b8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELocal%20success%20and%20political%20headaches%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMBC%20Studios%20has%20had%20some%20local%20success%20stories%2C%20like%20%26quot%3BRashash%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20show%20about%20a%20notorious%20criminal%20figure%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20that%20was%20well%20received%2C%20and%20%26quot%3BInheritance%2C%26quot%3B%20billed%20as%20the%20first%20Arab%20soap%20opera.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Sheikh%20Waleed%20Al%20Ibrahim%20%E2%80%94%20the%20politically%20connected%20founder%20of%20MBC%20Group%20%E2%80%94%20also%20wanted%20to%20make%20projects%20about%20historical%20events%2C%20which%20often%20courted%20controversy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20%26quot%3BMuawiya%2C%26quot%3B%20there%20was%20%26quot%3BEmbassy%2087%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20revisited%20the%20deadly%201987%20clash%20between%20Saudi%20police%20and%20Iranian%20pilgrims%20at%20Mecca.%20It%20was%20shelved.%20Then%20there%20was%20%26quot%3BFlight%20422%2C%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20hijacking%20of%20a%20Kuwaiti%20flight%20by%20Hezbollah.%20That%20one%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.middleeasteye.net%2Fdiscover%2Fkuwait-mbc-flight-422-why-was-cancelled%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremoved%20from%20streaming%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20Kuwait%20demanded%20it%20be%20taken%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHayek%2C%20the%20media%20consultant%2C%20said%20MBC%20Studios%20has%20to%20strike%20a%20tricky%20balance.%20It%20needs%20to%20embrace%20edgy%20topics%20to%20be%20relevant%20to%20audiences%20and%20fend%20off%20competitors%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-history-streaming-growth-story-hollywood-disruption-subscribers-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENetflix%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Amazon%20Prime.%20That%20means%20standing%20up%20to%20%26quot%3Bextremists%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bultra-conservatives%26quot%3B%20who%20want%20to%20censor%20its%20content%2C%20Hayek%20said.%20But%20it%20can't%20go%20too%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20push%20the%20envelope%20to%20the%20extreme%20of%20creating%20turbulence%20in%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227285%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22JEDDAH%2C%20SAUDI%20ARABIA%20-%20DECEMBER%2004%3A%20A%20general%20view%20of%20the%20Neom%20advertisement%20board%20at%20the%20Red%20Sea%20International%20Film%20Festival%202023%20on%20December%2004%2C%202023%20in%20Jeddah%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia.%20(Photo%20by%20Tim%20P.%20Whitby%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20The%20Red%20Sea%20International%20Film%20Festival)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f93a34c6ad288d147ded6d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESaudi%20Arabia%20promoted%20its%20Neom%20production%20facilities%20to%20international%20filmmakers.%3Cp%3ETim%20P.%20Whitby%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20The%20Red%20Sea%20International%20Film%20Festival%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22070fcf1c-e894-4b14-b240-d9922e71d016%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETurning%20away%20from%20Hollywood%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20challenges%2C%20in%20early%202024%2C%20MBC%20Group%20undertook%20an%20IPO%2C%20part%20of%20a%20boom%20of%20other%20Saudi%20public%20offerings.%20It%20was%20considered%20a%20big%20success%2C%20raising%20%24222%20million%20and%20valuing%20the%20company%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2024%2F01%2F08%2Fmedia%2Fsaudi-mbc-ipo-shares-soar%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enearly%20%243%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20prospectus%20promoting%20the%20offering%20touted%20the%20studio's%20relationships%20with%20Hollywood%20and%20its%20hiring%20of%20international%20talent.%20Behind%20the%20scenes%2C%20however%2C%20MBC%20Studios%20was%20pulling%20away%20from%20Hollywood%2C%20four%20people%20close%20to%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20IPO%2C%20MBC%20Studios%20has%20cut%20ties%20with%20many%20of%20the%20international%20players%20it%20leaned%20on.%20Those%20included%20the%20former%20Amazon%20exec%20who%20led%20its%20film%20and%20TV%20efforts%2C%20its%20head%20of%20global%20series%2C%20an%20Oscar-nominated%20producer%2C%20its%20longtime%20distributor%2C%20and%20talent%20giant%20CAA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20studio%20is%20now%20run%20by%20a%20veteran%20MBC%20executive%2C%20Samar%20Akrouk%2C%20and%20has%20cut%20back%20its%20ambitions%20to%20focus%20on%20lower-risk%20dramas%20and%20comedies%2C%20particularly%20productions%20for%20Shahid%2C%20its%20streaming%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20focused%20more%20on%20local%20language%20programs%20with%20local%20language%20budgets%20and%20putting%20the%20'Desert%20Warriors'%20and%20'Kandahars'%20on%20the%20back%20burner%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Cspan%3Ea%20person%20who%20has%20worked%20with%20the%20company%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20a%20time%20of%20transition%20at%20parent%20MBC%20Group%2C%20which%20replaced%20its%20CEO%20in%20early%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221c6fe330-8356-4b1c-b30d-234bd64064ca%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECrew%20and%20climate%20hurdles%20have%20held%20back%20Neom%20Media%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20MBC%20Studios%20has%20withdrawn%20from%20Hollywood%2C%20Neom%20Media%20has%20also%20faced%20challenges%20in%20attracting%20global%20productions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndustry%20insiders%20describe%20its%20facilities%20as%20top-notch%20but%20say%20its%20rebate%20of%20up%20to%2040%25%20on%20production%20costs%20%E2%80%94%20cash%20grants%20given%20to%20incentivize%20international%20and%20other%20productions%20to%20film%20there%20%E2%80%94%20is%20still%20unproven%20and%20hard%20to%20apply%20for.%20Those%20who%20get%20it%20could%20find%20the%20rebate%20benefit%20wiped%20out%20by%20the%20need%20to%20fly%20in%20crew%20members.%20Between%20Ramadan%20and%20the%20summer%20months%2C%20when%20the%20temperature%20exceeds%20100%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%2C%20shooting%20can%20be%20difficult%20for%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFilmmakers%20wanting%20a%20desert%20landscape%20may%20kick%20the%20tires%20on%20Saudi%20Arabia%20but%20often%20end%20up%20going%20to%20more%20established%20filmmaking%20locales%20like%20Jordan%2C%20Morocco%2C%20or%20Abu%20Dhabi%2C%20where%20%26quot%3BDune%3A%20Part%20Two%26quot%3B%20was%20shot.%20Some%20are%20put%20off%20by%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20alcohol%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETurmoil%20at%20the%20top%20can't%20have%20helped.%20Wayne%20Borg%2C%20an%20Australian%20exec%20who%20was%20tapped%20to%20run%20Neom%20Media%2C%20was%20replaced%20in%20September%20after%20a%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fbusiness%2Fthe-worlds-biggest-construction-project-is-a-magnet-for-executives-behaving-badly-9accd37b%3Fmod%3Darticle_inline%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20alleged%20he%20made%20racist%20and%20sexist%20comments%20about%20workers.%20Borg%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20multiple%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CANNES%2C%20FRANCE%20-%20MAY%2019%3A%20Wayne%20Borg%2C%20Managing%20Director%20of%20Media%2C%20Culture%20and%20Entertainment%2C%20Neom%20attends%20the%20Variety%20and%20Golden%20Globes%20Breakthrough%20Artists%20Party%20at%20Cannes%20Film%20Festival%20on%20May%2019%2C%202023%20in%20Cannes%2C%20France.%20(Photo%20by%20Victor%20Boyko%2FVariety%20via%20Getty%20Images)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f93a423fe8d3928362d73a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWayne%20Borg%2C%20former%20head%20of%20Neom%20Media%2C%20was%20replaced%20amid%20controversy%20around%20his%20leadership.%3Cp%3EVictor%20Boyko%2FVariety%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey've%20created%20the%20highway%20but%20haven't%20gotten%20the%20cars%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20top%20Hollywood%20agent%20who's%20worked%20extensively%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeom%20Media%20said%20it's%20in%20advanced%20discussions%20with%20unspecified%20international%20productions%20to%20film%20there%20in%202025.%20It%20touted%20the%20quality%20of%20its%20facilities%20and%20ease%20of%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20just%20attracting%20international%20productions%3B%20we're%20also%20becoming%20a%20hub%20for%20regional%20content%20and%20international%20content%2C%20with%20projects%20in%20the%20pipeline%2C%26quot%3B%20Michael%20Lynch%2C%20another%20Australian%20exec%20who%20now%20leads%20Neom%20Media%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20who%20have%20done%20business%20in%20the%20region%20preached%20patience.%20They%20compared%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20efforts%20to%20China's%20and%20Qatar's%20moves%20into%20entertainment%20and%20emphasized%20that%20it%20takes%20decades%20to%20build%20such%20a%20business.%20They%20said%20they%20see%20progress%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20especially%20considering%20it%20didn't%20even%20have%20movie%20theaters%20until%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%