0a%20human%20trafficking%20case.%20They%20are%20examining%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%2022-year-old%20woman%20and%20her%20infant%20being%20coerced%20into%20a%20scheme%20that%20allows%20him%20to%20be%20granted%20Argentine%20citizenship%20by%20having%20the%20child%20born%20in%20the%20South%20American%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPolice%20have%20arrested%20over%20a%20dozen%20Russian%20nationals%2C%20including%20Rudnev%2C%20who%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20religious%20group%2C%20CNN%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPregnant%20Woman%20Sparks%20Arrest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20investigation%20began%20after%20the%20Russian%20woman%20arrived%20at%20a%20hospital%20in%20the%20Patagonian%20city%20of%20Bariloche%20to%20give%20birth%20on%20March%2021.%20She%20was%20accompanied%20by%20two%20other%20women.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20was%20not%20their%20maiden%20visit%20as%20the%20hospital%20staff%20saw%20them%20four%20days%20earlier%20when%20they%20struggled%20to%20share%20how%20they%20were%20connected%20to%20the%20pregnant%20lady%20as%20well%20as%20their%20residence%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAs%20per%20Argentina's%20prosecutor%20and%20police%20reports%2C%20the%20pregnant%20woman%20looked%20nervous%20and%20malnourished%2C%20while%20she%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20speak%20much%20by%20her%20two%20companions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESoon%20after%2C%20the%20doctors%20were%20alarmed%20by%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20woman%20and%20her%20companions'%20behaviour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAfter%20the%20child%20was%20born%2C%20the%20two%20women%20asked%20the%20hospital%20authorities%20to%20document%20the%20newborn's%20last%20name%20as%20'Rudnev%2C'%20insisting%20that%20he%20was%20the%20father%20of%20the%20child%2C%20the%20prosecutor's%20report%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5C