0social%20media%20for%20his%20spoken%20English.%20Various%20clips%20and%20videos%20of%20his%20post-%20and%20pre-match%20interactions%20have%20gone%20viral%2C%20leading%20to%20trolls%20mocking%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Multan%20Sultans'%20captain%20addressed%20the%20criticism%20and%20trolls%20targeting%20him%20for%20his%20spoken%20English.%20During%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20he%20told%20reporters%2C%20as%20quoted%20from%20Geo%20News%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20regret%20not%20completing%20my%20education%2C%20which%20is%20why%20I%20don't%20know%20English%2C%20but%20I%20am%20not%20ashamed%20that%20as%20Pakistan's%20captain%2C%20I%20cannot%20speak%20English.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20demand%20from%20me%20is%20to%20play%20cricket%2C%20not%20to%20speak%20English.%20If%20Pakistan%20wanted%20English%2C%20I%20would%20become%20a%20professor%2C%20learn%20it%2C%20and%20return.%20But%20Pakistan%20asks%20me%20for%20cricket%2C%20not%20English%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERizwan%20shifted%20his%20focus%20to%20Pakistan's%20ongoing%20woes%20in%20the%20field%2C%20which%20have%20sparked%20criticism%20across%20the%20globe.%20Once%20considered%20to%20be%20an%20Asian%20powerhouse%2C%20the%20current%20Pakistan%20lot%20is%20chasing%20shadows%20of%20their%20former%20glory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarring%20their%20chaotic%20campaigns%20in%20the%20past%20ICC%20tournaments%2C%20Pakistan%20were%20truly%20exposed%20in%20the%20Champion%20Trophy%20organised%20on%20their%20home%20turf.%20The%20party%20organisers%20were%20the%20first%20to%20crash%20out%20of%20the%20tournament%20following%20back-to-back%20defeats%20against%20New%20Zealand%20and%20India%2C%20ending%20their%20title%20defence%20in%20the%20group%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20debacle%2C%20Pakistan%20toured%20New%20Zealand%20for%20five%20T20Is%20and%20three%20ODIs%20while%20keeping%20the%202026%20and%202027%20World%20Cups%20in%20the%20back%20of%20their%20minds.%20With%20a%20couple%20of%20new%20faces%2C%20Pakistan%20succumbed%20to%20a%204-1%20series%20defeat%20but%20remained%20optimistic%2C%20hoping%20to%20bounce%20back%20in%20the%20three%20ODIs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERizwan%20and%20Babar%20Azam%2C%20among%20the%20notable%20absentees%20in%20the%20T20Is%2C%20returned%20to%20the%20squad%2C%20but%20Pakistan's%20fate%20remained%20intact.%20An%20inexperienced%20New%20Zealand%20side%20whitewashed%20Pakistan%20by%20orchestrating%20a%203-0%20series%20triumph.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20suffered%20a%20lot%20of%20backlash%20after%20their%20unimpressive%20run.%20Amid%20the%20heavy%20criticism%20from%20fans%20and%20former%20cricketers%2C%20Rizwan%20urged%20the%20critics%20to%20offer%20solutions%20and%20guide%20them%20through%20the%20turbulent%20phase%2C%20leading%20to%20their%20improvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20fine%20to%20criticise%20the%20team%2C%20but%20also%20guide%20us%20on%20how%20to%20improve.%20Recently%2C%20during%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20Wasim%20Akram%20gave%20us%20advice.%20I%20wanted%20to%20talk%20more%20with%20him%2C%20but%20there%20wasn't%20enough%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERizwan%20acknowledged%20that%20fans%20have%20the%20right%20to%20be%20upset%20when%20the%20team%20fails%20to%20deliver%20and%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BFans%20are%20justified%20in%20their%20anger%2C%20and%20they've%20all%20the%20right%20to%20be%20upset%20at%20us%20because%20they%20also%20love%20us.%20But%20the%20Pakistan%20Super%20League%20(PSL)%20has%20given%20so%20much%20to%20Pakistan.%20Now%20it's%20time%20to%20enjoy%20the%20league.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744437840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F60glccl8_mohammad-rizwan-afp_625x300_01_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A