i%20Man%26quot%3B%20Who%20Knew%20Of%2026%2F11%20Attacks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2015%20years%20after%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20terror%20attack%2C%20anti-terror%20agency%20NIA%20is%20now%20zeroing%20in%20on%20an%20elusive%20figure%20who%20allegedly%20met%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Ftahawwur-rana%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETahawwur%20Rana%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20the%20key%20accused%2C%20in%20Dubai%20before%20the%20carnage.%20According%20to%20NIA%20sources%2C%20this%20person%20knew%20about%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERana%2C%20a%2064-year-old%20Pakistani-origin%20Canadian%20businessman%20and%20confidant%20of%20convicted%2026%2F11%20plotter%20David%20Coleman%20Headley%2C%20is%20now%20under%20high-security%20NIA%20custody%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20following%20his%20long-awaited%20extradition%20from%20the%20United%20States.%20His%20questioning%2C%20NIA%20officials%20believe%2C%20could%20finally%20unravel%20the%20'Dubai%20connection'%20to%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20terrorist%20attacks%20in%20India's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Man%20in%20Dubai%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20was%20the%20man%20that%20Rana%20met%20in%20Dubai%20before%20the%20Mumbai%20siege%20began%3A%20This%20individual%2C%20according%20to%20records%20shared%20by%20US%20investigative%20agencies%20with%20Indian%20authorities%2C%20knew%20about%20the%20impending%20attack.%20The%20NIA%20has%20confirmed%20that%20it%20is%20investigating%20the%20identity%20and%20role%20of%20this%20individual.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftahawwur-rana-mumbai-attacks-in-tahawwur-rana-probe-an-isi-link-and-two-names-major-iqbal-sameer-ali-8138926%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20Tahawwur%20Rana%20Probe%2C%20An%20ISI%20Link%2C%20And%20Two%20Names%3A%20Major%20Iqbal%2C%20Sameer%20Ali%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20NIA%20sources%2C%20Headley%20-%20also%20known%20as%20Daood%20Gilani%20-%20had%20explicitly%20warned%20Rana%20in%202008%20not%20to%20travel%20to%20India%2C%20hinting%20at%20imminent%20terrorist%20operations.%20Headley%20allegedly%20arranged%20for%20Rana%20to%20meet%20a%20co-conspirator%20in%20Dubai%20who%20confirmed%20the%20attack%20was%20imminent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20NIA%20sources%2C%20authorities%20are%20probing%20whether%20this%20individual%20was%20associated%20with%20the%20Inter-Services%20Intelligence%20(ISI)%2C%20Pakistan's%20military%20intelligence%20agency%2C%20a%20senior%20figure%20within%20the%20Pakistani%20Army%2C%20or%20a%20leader%20of%20a%20designated%20terror%20group%20operating%20from%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20NIA%2C%20the%20most%20intriguing%20element%20is%20that%20this%20individual's%20identity%20has%20been%20kept%20under%20wraps%20even%20within%20elite%20counter-terror%20networks.%20The%20agencies%20believe%20that%20Rana%20may%20have%20referred%20to%20him%20in%20earlier%20questioning%20by%20US%20authorities%2C%20whose%20classified%20reports%20are%20now%20in%20Indian%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Suspicious%20Lease%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20line%20of%20questioning%20revolves%20around%20a%20decision%20made%20by%20Rana%20and%20Headley%20in%20November%202008%3A%20neither%20renewed%20the%20lease%20of%20an%20office%20in%20Mumbai%20operated%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20Rana's%20immigration%20consultancy.%20This%20office%20was%20reportedly%20used%20as%20a%20cover%20by%20Headley%20to%20conduct%20reconnaissance%20of%20potential%20targets%2C%20including%20key%20hotels%20and%20public%20sites%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffirst-photo-of-us-marshalls-handing-over-tahawwur-rana-to-indian-officers-8137675%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFresh%20Images%20Show%20Tahawwur%20Rana%20Being%20Handed%20Over%20To%20Indian%20Officers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20previous%20NIA%20investigation%2C%20in%20August%202005%2C%20Headley%20had%20reportedly%20informed%20Rana%20about%20Lashkar-e-Taiba's%20(LeT)%20plan%20to%20send%20him%20to%20India%20to%20conduct%20reconnaissance%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20working%20for%20Rana's%20firm.%20Headley%20suggested%20that%20Rana's%20immigration%20business%20would%20be%20a%20suitable%20front%20to%20mask%20the%20activities%2C%20with%20Headley%20posing%20as%20a%20consultant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeadley's%20westernised%20appearance%20and%20US%20passport%20allowed%20him%20to%20move%20freely%2C%20surveying%20Mumbai's%20elite%20landmarks%2C%20video%20recording%20them%2C%20and%20sending%20the%20data%20back%20to%20his%20handlers%20in%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMultiple%20Indian%20Cities%20May%20Have%20Been%20Targets%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20NIA%20sources%2C%20the%20tactics%20used%20in%20Mumbai%20may%20have%20been%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20design%20to%20launch%20similar%20attacks%20in%20other%20Indian%20cities.%20As%20part%20of%20this%20inquiry%2C%20Rana's%20travel%20records%20are%20being%20examined%20closely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%20November%2013%20and%2021%20in%202008%2C%20Rana%20visited%20multiple%20Indian%20cities%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20Samraz%20Rana%20Akhtar.%20The%20cities%20include%20Hapur%20and%20Agra%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Kochi%2C%20Ahmedabad%2C%20and%20Mumbai.%20Authorities%20are%20investigating%20whether%20these%20trips%20were%20part%20of%20a%20reconnaissance%20mission%20to%20carry%20out%20similar%20attacks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Network%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20earlier%20stages%20of%20the%20investigation%2C%20the%20NIA%20named%20several%20individuals%20believed%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20broader%20conspiracy.%20These%20include%20Hafiz%20Saeed%2C%20founder%20of%20LeT%3B%20Zaki-ur-Rehman%20Lakhvi%2C%20operational%20commander%20of%20LeT%3B%20Sajjid%20Majid%3B%20Illyas%20Kashmiri%3B%20and%20Abdur%20Rehman%20Hashim%20Syed%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Major%20Abdurrehman%20or%20Pasha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20also%20alleged%20that%20these%20men%20worked%20in%20tandem%20with%20ISI%20officials%2C%20including%20individuals%20identified%20as%20Major%20Iqbal%20alias%20Major%20Ali%20and%20Major%20Sameer%20Ali%20alias%20Major%20Samir.%20All%20are%20suspected%20of%20playing%20roles%20in%20the%20planning%2C%20funding%2C%20and%20logistical%20execution%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERana%20and%20Headley%20attended%20military%20school%20together%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20later%20partnered%20in%20the%20immigration%20consultancy%20business%2C%20which%20authorities%20allege%20was%20used%20as%20a%20cover%20for%20terror%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigh-Security%20Custody%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERana%20is%20being%20held%20in%20a%20fortified%20cell%20at%20the%20NIA%20headquarters%20in%20the%20CGO%20complex%2C%20Delhi.%20Armed%20CRPF%20and%20Delhi%20Police%20personnel%20guard%20the%20outer%20perimeter.%20Inside%2C%20there%20is%20round-the-clock%20surveillance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%2024%20hours%2C%20a%20medical%20examination%20is%20conducted.%20Rana%20is%20allowed%20to%20meet%20his%20legal%20counsel%20on%20alternate%20days%20-%20but%20only%20under%20supervision%2C%20and%20only%20with%20a%20soft-tip%20pen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftahawwur-rana-nia-mumbai-attacks-14x14-ft-cell-24-hour-surveillance-how-tahawwur-rana-is-being-held-8139669%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E14x14%20Feet%20Cell%2C%2024-Hour%20Surveillance%3A%20How%20Tahawwur%20Rana%20Is%20Being%20Held%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20Director%20General%20of%20NIA%2C%20Sadanand%20Vasant%20Date%2C%2