t%20crackdown.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fhong-kongs-biggest-pro-democracy-party-moves-to-disband-as-freedoms-dwindle%2Farticleshow%2F120224477.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fhong-kongs-biggest-pro-democracy-party-moves-to-disband-as-freedoms-dwindle%2Famp_articleshow%2F120224477.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fhong-kongs-biggest-pro-democracy-party-moves-to-disband-as-freedoms-dwindle%2Famp_articleshow%2F120224477.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Zerodha%20CEO%20Tells%20Bill%20Gates%20%26quot%3BYou're%20Always%20In%20Hurry%26quot%3B.%20His%20Response%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20co-founder%20and%20billionaire%20philanthropist%20Bill%20Gates%20believes%20that%20people%20need%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20hard%20on%26quot%3B%20themselves%20if%20they%20wish%20to%20work%20hard%20and%20not%20fool%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Mr%20Gates%20appeared%20in%20Zerodha%20co-founder%20Nikhil%20Kamath's%20podcast%20series%20'People%20by%20WTF.%20'%20The%20two%20discussed%20a%20variety%20of%20subjects%20ranging%20from%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20to%20special%20relationship%20with%20India.%20The%20second%20part%20of%20their%20conversation%20was%20released%20on%20YouTube%20on%20Friday%2C%20April%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20show%2C%20Nikhil%20Kamath%20told%20Mr%20Gates%20that%20he%20always%20seems%20in%20a%20hurry%20whenever%20he%20is%20in%20India%20and%20asked%20whether%20he%20is%20hard%20on%20himself.%20He%20questioned%20the%20billionaire%20as%20to%20why%20he%20keeps%20running%20around%20%26quot%3Bso%20much%26quot%3B%20and%20meeting%20politicians%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%2C%20Mr%20Gates%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20fun.%20No%2C%20I%20think%20if%20you%20want%20to%20work%20hard%20and%20not%20fool%20yourself%2C%20you%20better%20be%20pretty%20hard%20on%20yourself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Microsoft%20co-founder%20has%20paid%20several%20visits%20to%20India%2C%20where%20he%20has%20held%20discussions%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Union%20Ministers%20JP%20Nadda%2C%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Puri%20and%20Jitendra%20Sing%2Ch%20among%20others.%20His%20most%20recent%20visit%20to%20the%20country%20was%20in%20March%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElsewhere%20in%20the%20podcast%2C%20Nikhil%20Kamath%20sought%20Bill%20Gates'%20views%20on%20whether%20a%20huge%20population%20is%20a%20boon%20or%20a%20bane%20from%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20capitalistic%20lens.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20reply%2C%20the%2069-year-old%20said%20that%20artificial%20intelligence%20would%20have%20%26quot%3Bchanged%20things%20enough%26quot%3B%20about%20two%20decades%20from%20now%20that%20it%20will%20%26quot%3Bfree%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20time%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20know%2C%20you%20can%20retire%20early%2C%20you%20can%20work%20shorter%20work%20weeks.%20It's%20gonna%20require%20almost%20a%20philosophical%20rethink%20about%2C%20okay%2C%20how%20should%20time%20be%20spent%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20what%20people%20will%20do%20if%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20work%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20have%20to%20work.%20I%20choose%20to%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gates%20thinks%20that%20it%20may%20not%20be%20that%20radical%20to%20think%20about%20whether%20people%20could%20retire%20at%2040.%20%26quot%3BBut%20if%20you%20said%20you%20never%20need%20to%20work%20at%20least%20to%20me...%20What%3F%20That%20is%20so%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20this%2C%20Nikhil%20Kamath%20said%20that%20people%20can%20look%20forward%20to%20figuring%20out%20a%20hierarchy%20that%20might%20not%20look%20like%20the%20current%20one%20but%20is%20%26quot%3Banother%20way%20to%20segregate%20ourselves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gates%20stated%20that%20the%20idea%20of%20pure%20communism%2C%20which%20is%20that%20everybody%20is%20totally%20the%20same%2C%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20unnatural%20behaviour%20for%20humans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20podcast%2C%20Nikhil%20Kamath%20even%20sought%20Bill%20Gates'%20views%20on%20his%20philanthropic%20works%2C%20asking%20how%20it%20%26quot%3Bmake%20sense%20to%20want%20to%20make%20money%20while%20you%20want%20to%20also%20give%20away%20money%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EFull%20Episode%208%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBillGates%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40BillGates%3C%2Fa%3E%20Part%202%3Cbr%3E%5CnLive%20now%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FM4ha3oFWko%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FM4ha3oFWko%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FbuX16cgTZa%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FbuX16cgTZa%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Nikhil%20Kamath%20(%40nikhilkamathcio)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnikhilkamathcio%2Fstatus%2F1910634139340202066%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2011%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20podcast%20series%20was%20launched%20by%20Kamath%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel%20last%20year%2C%20with%20Bill%20Gates%20being%20the%20first%20guest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20maiden%20episode%2C%20Bill%20Gates%20talked%20about%20his%20%26quot%3Bfantastic%20relationship%26quot%3B%20with%20India%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bamazing%20people%26quot%3B%20he%20works%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744433580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fed24dq1s_bill-gates-nikhil_625x300_12_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia