tiative%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fexternal-affairs-defence-security%2Fnews%2Fus-vp-jd-vance-nsa-mike-waltz-visit-india-trust-initiative-family-125041200171_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tahawwur%20Rana%20On%20Suicide%20Watch%20In%20NIA%20Custody%2C%20Only%20Allowed%20Soft-Tip%20Pen%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks%20co-conspirator%20Tahawwur%20Rana%20was%20extradited%20to%20India%20and%20sent%20to%2018-day%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20custody%2C%20he%20remains%20on%20suicide%20watch%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20Of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Rana%20is%20being%20kept%20in%20a%20highly%20secure%20cell%20within%20the%20NIA%20headquarters%20and%20is%20under%2024%2F7%20human%20and%20CCTV%20surveillance.%20He%20is%20allowed%20to%20only%20use%20a%20soft-tip%20pen%20and%20meet%20his%20lawyer%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20NIA%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2014%20feet%20by%2014%20feet%20located%20on%20the%20ground%20floor%20of%20the%20NIA%20building%2C%20Rana%20is%20monitored%20by%20multiple-layered%20digital%20security%20systems%2C%20only%2012%20designated%20NIA%20officers%20are%20authorised%20to%20enter%20and%20all%20basic%20needs%20-%20meals%2C%20drinking%20water%2C%20medical%20provisions%20-%20are%20being%20delivered%20to%20him%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20headquarters%20have%20been%20turned%20into%20a%20fortress%20since%20Rana's%20arrival.%20Additional%20Delhi%20Police%20and%20paramilitary%20personnel%20have%20been%20deployed%20and%20no%20one%20is%20permitted%20entry%20without%20clearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERana%2C%20a%20Pakistani-Canadian%2C%20arrived%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Thursday%20months%20after%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20said%20after%20a%20meeting%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20that%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks%20accused%20will%20be%20extradited.%20He%20finally%20landed%20in%20Delhi%20after%20he%20exhausted%20all%20legal%20options%20to%20challenge%20his%20extradition%20from%20the%20US.%20Judge%20Chander%20Jit%20Singh%2C%20presiding%20over%20the%20special%20NIA%20bench%2C%20granted%20the%20NIA%2018%20days'%20custody%20of%20Rana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccused%20of%20masterminding%20the%20November%2026%2C%202008%20attacks%2C%20that%20killed%20166%20people%2C%20Rana%20will%20be%20interrogated%20to%20uncover%20the%20%26quot%3Bdeeper%20layers%20of%20the%20conspiracy%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERana%20has%20to%20be%20confronted%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20evidence%20and%20his%20statements%20would%20lead%20to%20%26quot%3Badditional%20discoveries%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20NIA%20submitted.%20The%20agency%20further%20told%20the%20court%20it%20needed%20to%20investigate%20his%20links%20with%20other%20terrorists%20and%20those%20accused%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20attack%20case%2C%20Rana%2C%20who%20is%20a%20close%20associate%20of%2026%2F11%20main%20conspirator%20David%20Coleman%20Headley%20alias%20Daood%20Gilani%2C%20a%20US%20citizen%2C%20is%20accused%20of%20conspiring%20with%20the%20latter%20and%20operatives%20of%20designated%20terrorist%20organisations%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20(LeT)%20and%20Harkat-ul-Jihadi%20Islami%20(HUJI)%20along%20with%20other%20Pakistan-based%20co-conspirators%2C%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20three-day%20terror%20siege%20of%20India's%20financial%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NIA's%20interrogation%20is%20focused%20on%20getting%20more%20details%20on%20his%20possible%20connection%20with%20Pakistan-based%20LeT%2C%20as%20well%20as%20his%20suspected%20links%20with%20the%20officials%20of%20Pakistan%20spy%20agency%20Inter-Services%20Intelligence%20(ISI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20further%20said%20that%20as%20part%20of%20the%20probe%20to%20piece%20together%20crucial%20evidence%20and%20retrace%20events%20from%2017%20years%20ago%20Ran