%20bracelet%20to%20stadium%20dates%20and%20surprise%20stage%20appearances%2C%20Taylor%20Swift%20and%20Travis%20Kelce's%20romance%20has%20captivated%20the%20world.%20Their%20relationship%20blossomed%20from%20a%20podcast%20shout-out%20to%20public%20declarations%20of%20love%2C%20including%20lyrical%20changes%20and%20heartfelt%20acknowledgments%20at%20award%20shows.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Ftaylor-swift-and-travis-kelces-relationship-timeline-from-friendship-bracelets-to-surprise-stage-appearances%2Farticleshow%2F120207084.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Can't%20Follow%20Judicial%20Timelines'%3A%20Team%20Trump%20vs%20Judge%20Over%20Wrong%20Deportation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20rejected%20a%20federal%20judge's%20order%20to%20provide%20by%20Friday%20a%20status%20update%20on%20a%20wrongly%20deported%20Salvadoran%20migrant's%20return%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20calling%20the%20deadline%20%26quot%3Bimpracticable%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BForeign%20affairs%20cannot%20operate%20on%20judicial%20timelines%2C%20in%20part%20because%20it%20involves%20sensitive%20country-specific%20considerations%20wholly%20inappropriate%20for%20judicial%20review%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20administration%20attorneys%20wrote%20in%20a%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawyers%20for%20Salvadoran%20immigrant%20Kilmar%20Abrego%20Garcia%2C%20in%20their%20own%20filing%2C%20expressed%20outrage%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Barrogance%20and%20cruelty%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Trump%20administration%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20continuing%20to%20%26quot%3Bdelay%2C%20obfuscate%20and%20flout%20court%20orders%20while%20a%20man's%20life%20and%20safety%20is%20at%20risk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20Friday%20hearing%20that%20lasted%20barely%20half%20an%20hour%2C%20district%20judge%20Paula%20Xinis%20said%20the%20government%20had%20%26quot%3Bfailed%20to%20comply%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20would%20have%20to%20file%20a%20declaration%20on%20Abrego%20Garcia's%20status%20%26quot%3Beach%20day...%20until%20further%20order%26quot%3B%2C%20starting%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20further%20scheduled%20a%20new%20in-person%20hearing%20for%20April%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbrego%20Garcia%2C%20a%20Salvadoran%20living%20in%20the%20eastern%20state%20of%20Maryland%20and%20married%20to%20a%20US%20citizen%2C%20was%20arrested%20March%2012%20by%20immigration%20police.%20He%20was%20among%20more%20than%20200%20people%20deported%20on%20March%2015%20to%20a%20notorious%20prison%20in%20El%20Salvador%20as%20part%20of%20Donald%20Trump's%20migration%20crackdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbrego%20Garcia's%20family%20has%20continued%20to%20proclaim%20his%20innocence%2C%20and%20a%20Trump%20administration%20lawyer%20has%20acknowledged%20that%20his%20expulsion%20followed%20an%20%26quot%3Badministrative%20error.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESupreme%20Court%20battle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20federal%20court%20had%20ruled%20in%202019%20that%20he%20could%20not%20be%20expelled%20to%20El%20Salvador%2C%20where%20his%20life%20could%20be%20in%20danger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20has%20said%20it%20is%20powerless%20to%20secure%20Abrego%20Garcia's%20return%20and%20insisted%20he%20was%20part%20of%20MS-13%2C%20a%20Salvadoran%20gang%20the%20United%20States%20classified%20as%20terrorist%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20judge%20Xinis%20said%20she%20had%20seen%20no%20evidence%20Abrego%20Garcia%20was%20a%20gang%20member%20and%20ordered%20the%20government%20to%20%26quot%3Beffectuate%26quot%3B%20his%20return%20to%20the%20United%20States%20by%20April%207%20at%20the%20latest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conservative-dominated%20Supreme%20Court%20later%20held%20that%20the%20administration%20was%20indeed%20required%20to%20%26quot%3Bfacilitate%26quot%3B%20Garcia's%20return%20and%20to%20ensure%20that%20he%20be%20treated%20as%20if%20he%20had%20never%20been%20wrongly%20deported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20justices%20also%20directed%20Xinis%20to%20clarify%20her%20order%20--%20saying%20she%20may%20have%20exceeded%20her%20authority%20and%20needed%20to%20reflect%20%26quot%3Bdue%20regard%20for%20the%20deference%20owed%20to%20the%20Executive%20Branch%20in%20the%20conduct%20of%20foreign%20affairs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20subsequently%20amended%20her%20wording%20to%20say%20the%20government%20must%20take%20%26quot%3Ball%20available%20steps%20to%20facilitate%26quot%3B%20his%20return%20%26quot%3Bas%20soon%20as%20possible%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20point%2C%20Xinis%20also%20directed%20the%20administration%20to%20provide%20an%20update%20on%20Abrego%20Garcia's%20current%20location%20and%20detention%20status%2C%20and%20to%20explain%20by%20Friday%20the%20legal%20grounds%20on%20which%20he%20was%20detained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETest%20of%20power%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20hearing%20Friday%2C%20the%20Trump%20administration%20said%20it%20needed%20more%20time%2C%20requesting%20an%20April%2015%20date%20for%20response%20to%20the%20judge's%20questions%20and%20a%20postponement%20of%20the%20hearing%20to%20April%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EXinis%20refused%2C%20maintaining%20Friday's%20hearing%20and%20extending%20the%20deadline%20to%20provide%20an%20update%20within%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20wrote%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bunable%20to%20provide%20the%20information...%20on%20the%20impracticable%20deadline%20set%20by%20the%20Court.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20those%20expelled%20along%20with%20Abrego%20Garcia%20were%20accused%20by%20the%20administration%20of%20belonging%20to%20a%20Venezuelan%20gang%2C%20Tren%20de%20Aragua%2C%20which%20Washington%20has%20labeled%20a%20terrorist%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20represents%20the%20only%20time%20the%20administration%20has%20acknowledged%20wrongly%20deporting%20anyone%2C%20though%20the%20Justice%20Department%20subsequently%20suspended%20the%20lawyer%20who%20made%20that%20concession%2C%20saying%20he%20had%20failed%20to%20vigorously%20defend%20the%20government%20position.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20has%20described%20the%20case%20as%20a%20key%20test%20of%20the%20president's%20power%20to%20conduct%20sensitive%20national%20security-related%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744426860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Ftj8sulqg_kilmar-abrego-garcia_625x300_12_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkilmar-abrego-garcia-team-trump-vs-judge-over-wrong-deportation-to-el-salvador-cant-follow-judicial-timelines-8145223%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Trump%20administration%20rejected%20a%20federal%20judge's%20order%20to%20provide%20by%20Friday%20a%20status%20update%20on%20a%20wrongly%20deported%20Salvadoran%20migrant's%20return%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20calling%20the%20deadline%20%26quot%3Bimpracticable%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkilmar-abrego-garcia-team-trump-vs-judge-over-wrong-deportation-to-el-salvador-cant-follow-judicial-timelines-8145223%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bill%20Maher%20Praises%20President%20Trump%20as%20%E2%80%98Gracious%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Not%20Fake%E2%80%99%20Recounting%20His%20White%20House%20Visit%3A%20%E2%80%98Everything%20I%E2%80%99ve%20Ever%20Not%20Liked%20About%20Him%20Was%20Absent%E2%8