20a%20tracker%20with%20her%20dogs%2C%20says%20that%20microchipping%20and%20GPS%20trackers%20work%20together%20like%20locking%20your%20doors%20and%20installing%20a%20home%20security%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20more%20about%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Four-expertise-in-pets-insider-pet-care-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehow%20Business%20Insider%20Reviews%20tests%20and%20researches%20pet%20products%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ae418845-603a-480b-89b9-13653a4757dd%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Our%20top%20picks%20for%20the%20best%20GPS%20dog%20trackers%5C%22%3EOur%20top%20picks%20for%20the%20best%20dog%20GPS%20trackers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20overall%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFi%20Series%203%20-%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15109047881xui-20%26h%3D6354f8a64000109ca7395e990e1c9d5f693cb7c028ff995bdf0598d257ffcdc9%26postID%3D67f4190e3d37c2e3ad3cfaa5%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-gps-pet-trackers%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB0CVN2R7MB%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESee%20Amazon%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20activity%20tracking%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhistle%20Go%20Explore%202.0%20Smart%20Tracker%20-%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15109047881xui-20%26h%3Dbc58a5a33567e008797cf5c454cb66afcef3781f67b41314acb26fd0734d249d%26postID%3D67f4190e3d37c2e3ad3cfaa5%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-gps-pet-trackers%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chewy.com%252Fwhistle-go-explore-dog-gps-tracker%252Fdp%252F277143%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESee%20at%20Chewy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20budget%3A%20%3C%2Fstr