rea%2C%20which%20Nwuneli%20described%20as%20a%20slum%2C%20is%20flood-prone.%20Indeed%2C%20many%20of%20the%20surrounding%20houses%20are%20built%20on%20stilts%2C%20she%20said.%20So%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20donations%20and%20volunteers%2C%20Nwuneli's%20NGO%20planted%20flood-resistant%20trees%20around%20the%20playground%20%E2%80%94%20among%20300%20trees%20she%20says%20they%20planted%20across%20the%20wider%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20first%20homed%20in%20on%20this%20dump%20site%20in%20November.%20On%20March%201%2C%20they%20opened%20the%20park%20for%20schoolchildren.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20remember%20when%20the%20children%20were%20like%2C%20'now%20something%20we%20can%20actually%20call%20beautiful.'%20It%20kind%20of%20broke%20my%20heart%2C%26quot%3B%20Nwuneli%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20eyes%2C%20though%2C%20this%20is%20just%20a%20pilot%20park.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2294e36a2a-1564-4a05-9675-cae95faf59c1%5C%22%3EA%20Central%20Park%20for%20Lagos%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Earth%20Prize%20funding%2C%20Nwuneli%20is%20planning%20three%20more%20parks.%20They%20won't%20be%20playgrounds%20like%20the%20one%20that%20opened%20in%20March%2C%20she%20says%2C%20but%20multi-functional%20community%20hubs%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Furban-farming-gardening-carbon-footpring-study-produce-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egardens%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20greenhouses%2C%20and%20waste%20collection%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20aiming%20to%20convert%20a%20large%20landfill%20in%20Lagos%2C%20pending%20government%20approval.%20For%20the%20other%20two%20parks%2C%20she's%20targeting%20the%20neighboring%20Nigerian%20states%20of%20Ogun%20and%20Oyo%2C%20which%20are%20also%20experiencing%20floods%20and%20droughts%20that%20will%20likely%20get%20worse%20as%20global%20temperatures%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20satisfied.%20I%20feel%20like%20every%20community%20needs%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Nwuneli%20said.%3C%2