ngry-people-tesla-elon-musk-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrivers%20are%20being%20flipped%20off%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Owners%20who%20just%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20cool%20car%20are%20stuck%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcybertruck-drivers-face-damages-repairs-mardi-gras-parade-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emaking%20some%20sort%20of%20political%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20they%20wanted%20to%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20kids%2C%20it's%20a%20different%20story.%20Kids%20%3Cem%3Elove%3C%2Fem%3E%20Cybertrucks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20makes%20sense.%20First%20of%20all%2C%20kids%20love%20trucks!%20For%20a%20preschooler%2C%20passing%20by%20an%20active%20construction%20site%20is%20like%20being%20a%20VIP%20at%20Coachella.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Cybertruck%20is%20big%2C%20it's%20distinctive.%20It's%20rare.%20Seeing%20one%20on%20the%20road%20or%20even%20in%20a%20parking%20lot%20is%20a%20head-turner.%20It%20looks%20like%20it%20was%20made%20in%20Minecraft%20or%20out%20of%20Legos.%20It's%20absolutely%20aesthetically%20thrilling%20for%20a%20demographic%20that%20can't%20yet%20tie%20shoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%206-year-old%20loves%20Teslas%20but%20has%20no%20idea%20who%20Musk%20is%2C%20and%20that's%20intentional%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mandy%20Shobar%2C%20a%20parent%20of%20two%20boys%20in%20Castro%20Valley%2C%20California.%20Shobar%20herself%20is%20not%20a%20fan%20of%20Telsa's%20CEO%20for%20reasons%20that%20would%20make%20sense%20to%20other%20adults%20but%20not%20a%20kindergartener.%20Her%20older%20son%2C%209%2C%20is%20less%20excited%20about%20the%20Cybertruck.%20%26quot%3BHe%20says%20they%20look%20'glitchy.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20Business%20Insider%20office%2C%20parents%20also%20noted%20their%20kids%20were%20obsessed%20with%20Cybertrucks.%20My%20boss's%20first%20grader%20recently%20brought%20home%20a%20piece%20of%20art%20from%20school%20dedicated%20to%20the%20EV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20kid's%20drawing%20of%20a%20cybertruck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f9385d3fe8d3928362d697%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%207-year-old's%20artistic%20rendering%20of%20a%20Tesla%20Cybertruck.%3Cp%3EDash%20Herrin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20own%20kids%20get%20excited%20when%20they%20see%20a%20Cybertruck.%20My%20son%20went%20through%20a%20phase%20when%20he%20was%20around%206%20or%207%20when%20he%20was%20fascinated%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20character%2C%20and%20even%20brought%20home%20a%20book%20from%20the%20school%20library%20about%20Teslas.%20(The%20book%2C%20from%202018%2C%20didn't%20include%20too%20much%20about%20Musk%20himself.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImagine%20this%20through%20a%20child's%20eyes%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-ceo-elon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20richest%20man%20in%20the%20world%20who%20makes%20rockets%20and%20cool-looking%20cars.%20How%20could%20you%20not%20be%20intrigued%3F%20Kids%20are%20obsessed%20with%20superlatives%3A%20the%20fastest%2C%20the%20biggest%2C%20the%20most.%20It's%20why%20everyone%20knows%20the%20blue%20whale%20is%20the%20biggest%2C%20and%20the%20cheetah%20is%20the%20fastest.%20Kids%20talk%20about%20Usain%20Bolt's%20speed%20with%20reverence%20and%20compare%20heights%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftallest-building-burj-khalifa-dubai-photo-tour-review-worth-it%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBurj%20Khalifa%3C%2Fa%3E%20(which%2C%20to%20be%20honest%2C%20I%20only%20learned%20is%20the%20world's%20tallest%20building%20from%20my%20own%20kid).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b6ef680f-f09f-43dc-8368-300c56fc5ae6%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%20is%20becoming%20less%20popular%20with%20adults%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20idea%20that%20Musk%20is%20controversial%20because%20of%20his%20political%20opinions%20and%20role%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-department-of-government-efficiency%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDOGE%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20not%20really%20something%20that%20is%20easily%20explained%20to%20a%20small%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20too%20many%20years%20ago%20that%20Musk%20seemed%20like%20an%20unproblematic%20aspirational%20STEM%20figure%20for%20young%20kids.%20But%20with%20his%20involvement%20in%20the%202024%20election%20and%20now%20DOGE%2C%20the%20public's%20perception%20of%20Musk%20has%20changed.%20According%20to%20Nate%20Silver's%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.natesilver.net%2Fp%2Felon-musk-polls-popularity-nate-silver-bulletin%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Silver%20Bulletin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Musk's%20favorability%20polling%20switched%20from%20positive%20to%20negative%20last%20summer%2C%20and%20he's%20now%20less%20popular%20than%20ever%20%E2%80%94%20with%2053.5%25%20%26quot%3Bunfavorable%26quot%3B%20ratings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETom%20Cook%20(no%20relation%20to%20Tim)%20isn't%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETelsa%3C%2Fa%3E%20hater%20%E2%80%94%20he%20previously%20owned%20a%20Model%203.%20He%20thinks%20the%20Cybertruck%2C%20however%2C%20is%20aesthetically%20unpleasing.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20some%20technical%20aspects%20of%20it%20that%20are%20good%20(electrical%20components%20where%20Tesla%20does%20good%20engineering)%2C%20but%20the%20nexus%20of%20cost%2Fpracticality%2Flooks%2Fassociation%20with%20%5BMusk%5D%20make%20it%20just%20impossible%20to%20ever%20take%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20Cook%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20he%20was%20surprised%20when%20his%203-year-old%20daughter%20made%20a%20piece%20o